No.

28
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:10,290
You have no choice!

29
00:04:12,110 --> 00:04:14,410
You'll pay a heavy price.

30
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,810
Nice imposing manner.

31
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:27,630
But...

32
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:03,860
