♪ Awakening this extraordinary destiny ♪

50
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:50,420
♪ Awakening another version of myself ♪

51
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:56,169
♪ The clearest, most resilient eyes of yours ♪

52
00:06:56,170 --> 00:07:00,420
